&lt;p&gt;And a same crash was reported a long time ago. &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.hpdd.intel.com/browse/LU-1311?focusedCommentId=35871&amp;amp;page=com.atlassian.jira.plugin.system.issuetabpanels:comment-tabpanel#comment-35871&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://jira.hpdd.intel.com/browse/LU-1311?focusedCommentId=35871&amp;amp;page=com.atlassian.jira.plugin.system.issuetabpanels:comment-tabpanel#comment-35871&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There was a important log there:&lt;br/&gt;
Apr 30 08:21:41 barry-oss4 kernel: &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;247839.213070&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; wanted to write 1008 but wrote -5&lt;/p&gt;</description>
